title: #92Noon! Vox In The Box: Bruce Boudreau, Michael Russo, Ryan Carter, Bill Guerin, Rachel Ramsey
description: The undefeated Vox In The Box is back! Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau joins the show at the start, Michael Russo talks Zucker trade, Former Wild and White Bear Lake Bear Ryan Carter brings his perspective about the Wild to the box, and Wild GM Bill Guerin stops by to talk about his first move, and Pronger with a Ponytail Rachel Ramsey stops by!
